{
  "__comments": [
    "=================================================================",
    "Docker Container Logs via Loki",
    "=================================================================",
    "",
    "REQUIRED SETUP:",
    "- Loki datasource configured in Grafana",
    "- Promtail scraping Docker container logs",
    "",
    "PROMTAIL CONFIGURATION:",
    "Promtail must be configured to scrape Docker logs:",
    "  scrape_configs:",
    "    - job_name: docker",
    "      docker_sd_configs:",
    "        - host: unix:///var/run/docker.sock",
    "      relabel_configs:",
    "        - source_labels: ['__meta_docker_container_name']",
    "          target_label: 'container'",
    "",
    "NOTES:",
    "- Simple log viewer for all Docker containers",
    "- Use Grafana's log panel filters for searching",
    "- Adjust time range as needed",
    "================================================================="
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "editable": true,
